        "Description": "German entrepreneur Ulrich Gloeckner arrived at the Himmapan earlier this morning. We fear this is to meet up with Jack Torrent, a gardener employeed at the hotel. These two individuals have communicated regarding a poison that is currently being made. They are meeting in order to study a pesticide, a toxic proudct that they could be inspired by.\r\rIn order to prevent this exchange, you need to eliminate the two malicious men, and obtain the insecticide from the exterminator&apos;s van.\r\rGood luck.",
